---
title: Herby Pork Meatballs & Garden Salad with Creamy Pesto Dressing & Onion Chutney
description: For pork meatballs with some Mediterranean vibes, lace them with our rich herb seasoning. Then add an extra layer of flavour by coating them in our onion chutney before serving over a simple and textural salad to balance out the richness. Don't forget the drizzle of creamy pesto dressing to tie everything together.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
